data.meta_description: The Asian Institute of Research Journal of Health and Medical Sciences is a peer-reviewed International Journal of the Asian Institute of Research. The journal covers scholarly articles in the fields of Medicine and Public Health. Indexed in EBSCO, Index Copernicus, Google Scholar, ZENODO
